<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="million-num">million <strong><em>num</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'mɪljən/    美 /'mɪljən/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>一百万</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tens of thousands of cows would never give milk again. <strong>Half a million</strong> pigs and <strong>millions of</strong> chickens were dead.
成千上万的奶牛不再产奶，五十万头猪和千百万只小鸡全都死了。</p><footer>人教① – 4</footer></div></div>